    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="contact-text-content">
            <p>
                Have a question about our collections or need assistance finding your perfect fit?
                Our dedicated concierge team is here to provide you with a seamless and
                personalized shopping experience. Whether you require styling advice or have
                inquiries regarding your order, we invite you to reach out to us.
            </p>
            <p>
                At ÉLÉGANCE, we are committed to excellence in service, ensuring that every
                interaction is as refined as our footwear. Connect with us today and let us
                help you step into a world of timeless luxury.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-button-wrapper">
            <a href="mailto:support@elegance.com" class="btn-contact">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

